window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The end is finally here. </b></p> <p>Morgan and Sarah rush back to the Five Kingdoms, with the survivors of Faeland in tow, as enemies converge on all sides. Gods and monsters alike threaten to destroy the world, and there is only one person mighty enough to stop them all.</p> <p>Morgan will be tested like never before, in his final bid to free the planet of the chaotic influences that threaten to destroy it. Will he prove, once and for all, that he is truly Omniscient? Or, will one of his many enemies finally put an end to the King of Eternity?</p> <p>Warning: this audiobook contains some profanity, gore, and content that may not be suitable for children. This audiobook also contains GameLit elements, such as stat sheets, a form of leveling, and experience gain.</p>"; 
